Firayim Minista na Indiya zai halarci bude sabon ginin majami'a a yankin da ake takaddama a kansa
SABUWAR DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin kafa kasa mai zuwa a watan gobe don gidan ibada na Hindu a wani yanki da ake takaddama a kansa a arewacin Indiya inda wasu masu tsattsauran ra'ayin Hindu suka rusa wani masallaci a karni na 16 a 1992, bisa ga amintar da ke kula ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya taron suka zai ce yana da matukar alfanu ga mabiya addinin Hindu amma kuma hakan ya cika shekara guda kenan da Majalisar Dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin ta mai cin gashin kai na jiharta daya tilo da ke da rinjayen a garin Musulmai, Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba ta yiwu a rasa ba ga magoya baya da kuma masu hamayya da Modi ta dan kishin Hindu na Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda gabatarwar tasa ta kwashe shekaru da dama sun hada da alkawurran da suka yi na kwace ikon Kashmir na cin gashin kai da kuma gina gidan ibada ga gunkin Hindu Ram inda masallacin zamanin Mughal ya ke. da zarar ya tsaya, wani wuri a cikin garin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu ba da gaskiya suka yi imanin cewa mahaifar Ram ce.
Saboda kwayar cutar ta coronavirus tana ci gaba da yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wacce ta bayar da rahoto a karo na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye ta gidan talabijin din kasar kuma adadin mahalarta da 'yan kallo zai takaita, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma World Hindu Organisation. , kungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
Majami'ar zata kasance a matsayin "cibiya mai dorewa da rashin dawwamammen hadin kai na zamantakewar al'umma, hadin kan kasa da hadewa da kuma tada jijiyoyin Hindutva," ko hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji kakakin kungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar a ranar Asabar.
An warware takaddama na tsawon shekaru da dama a kan shafin a bara bayan nasarar da BJP ta samu a babban zaben.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukunci a kan amincewa da haikalin, tana mai cewa za a ba Musulmi koken biyar a wani wurin daban.
Gogaggun Mabiya addinin Hindu sun daɗe suna jayayya cewa maharan musulmai masu mugunta sun gina masallaci a saman wani gidan ibada mai fa'ida a tsohuwar garin Ayodya
Zanga-zangar Disamba na 1992 bayan lalata masallacin ya haifar da rikicin kabilanci inda aka kashe kusan mutane 2,000, wanda galibi Musulmai ne.
A halin yanzu haka, ana ci gaba da sauraron shari'ar kotun rusau a wata kotu ta musamman.
Wani mai zane daga Ahmedabad, Gujarat, asalin garin Modi, ya gabatar da wani katafaren ginin yashi mai tsawon ƙafa 161 (mita 49) tare da ƙauyuka biyar.
Yogi Adityanath, babban wazirin Uttar Pradesh kuma wani malamin addinin Hindu, ya bukaci Ayodhya da ta gudanar da bikin tsaftacewa da tsarkakewa na musamman sannan kuma duk gidajen ibadar garin su kunna fitilun mai kafin ziyarar Modi, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Press Trust na Indiya.
Adityanath ya ce bikin ya nuna karshen gwagwarmayar "shekara 500," in ji PTI.
