An kona Kotu a lokacin zanga-zanga a Kalifoniya
OAKLAND, Ca. - Masu zanga-zanga a Kalifoniya sun cinna wuta a wata kotu, sun lalata wani ofishin ‘yan sanda tare da cin zarafin jami’ai bayan wata zanga-zangar lumana ta kara karfi a yammacin Asabar,‘ yan sandan Oakland sun ce.
Masu zanga-zangar sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa rubutu a jikin zane, sun yi harbi da tartsatsin wuta da kuma nuna wuta a kan jami'ai, in ji sashen na Oakland a shafin Twitter.
Tweets da yawa sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shirya "don taimaka mana samar da wurare masu aminci da wuraren tsaro ga masu zanga-zangar."
Zanga-zangar ta fara ne da yammacin ranar Asabar tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Bangon uwaye," kwatankwacin rukuni wanda ya kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke fuskantar wakilan Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan garin don tsaron gidan kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya tura wakilai na tarayya don yin dandazo kan zanga-zangar da ke faruwa a dare tun daga mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
Zanga-zangar a Oakland ta fara cikin lumana, amma daga baya ta rikide ta zama ta dare.
‘Yan sanda sun ayyana“ haramtacciyar taro ”da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare. kuma jami'ai sun nemi taron jama'a su watse.
Wutar ta tashi ne a Babban Kotun Alameda County kuma an dauke ta jim kadan bayan haka, kafafen yada labarai sun ruwaito.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci suna "fasa tagogi suna rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata ga mazauna wurin."
Hotunan da sashen ya wallafa a shafin twitter sun nuna fasassun gilasai da fenti fantsama a ginin ‘yan sanda.
An Samu Tsaron Tsaro a Wajen Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu, China
Akwai tsauraran matakan tsaro a wajen karamin ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu, China Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurkan ke shirin barin harabar.
An ga manyan motoci guda uku masu motsi suna shiga harabar ginin, yayin da ‘yan sanda sanye da kayan farin kaya suka yi layi duka bangarorin titin, wadanda aka yi musu shinge da karfe.
Editan jaridar ta Times Times ta China ya wallafa a shafinsa na Tweeter cewa an bai wa karamin ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu awanni 72 ya rufe, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta tuhumi cewa wasu ma'aikata a karamin ofishin jakadancin Chengdu "suna gudanar da ayyukan da ba su dace da asalinsu ba."
Ba tare da bayar da wani cikakken bayani ba, kakakin ma'aikatar harkokin wajen China, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya tsoma baki cikin harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da muradunta na tsaro.
Umarnin da China ta bayar na rufe karamin ofishin jakadancin a Chengdu ya fito ne a ranar Juma’a a matsayin ramuwar gayya ga umarnin da Amurka ta bayar na rufe karamin ofishin jakadancin China da ke Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare hikimar Amurkawa da bayanan sirri na Amurkawa."
Yayin da rufe karamin ofishin jakadancin China a Houston ya fara aiki a ranar Juma’a, an ga wasu gungun maza wadanda suka bayyana su jami’an Amurka ne suna kutsawa cikin ginin ta kofar baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar din da ta keta yarjejeniyoyin kasa da kasa da na bangarorin biyu kuma China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da bayyana yadda za ta yi ba.
Rufe titin-da-tat ya kara dagula rikice-rikicen da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan da suka shafi kasuwanci da leken asirin masana’antu zuwa hakkin dan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban masu adawa da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoton Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da ‘yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ke buya a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na haramtacciyar kungiyar Taliban ce ta Pakistan da ke da alhakin kai hari kan sojojin Pakistan da kuma fararen hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta yi cudanya da reshen Afghanistan da ke kungiyar IS.
Wasu daga cikin membobin TTP har sun shiga kungiyar ta IS, wacce ke da hedikwata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta ba da amsa ba a ranar Lahadi ga buƙatun da Kamfanin Dillancin Labarai na Associated Press ya yi don yin sharhi.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, da aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ya sha da kyar daga jami’an tsaron Afghanistan da na Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokutan kungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan.
Rahoton ya fito ne daga kungiyar bincike da sanya takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wacce ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta membobin kungiyar ta IS a Afghanistan da 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancin ta ya kare, har yanzu kungiyar ta IS tana cikin shugabannin ta wani dan kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa idon ta samu labarin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin kungiyar ta Daular Islama, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, ba da jimawa ba suka isa Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Kodayake a cikin ja da baya, (daular musulinci) tana nan tana iya aiwatar da manyan hare-hare a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakanan yana da nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka, "in ji rahoton, tana magana kan yarjejeniyar zaman lafiyar Amurka da aka sanya wa hannu tare da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An kulla wannan yarjejeniyar ce don ba wa Amurka damar kawo karshen shiga tsakani na shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ta yi kira ga Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa kungiyoyin ‘yan ta’adda ba za su yi amfani da yankin nata ba.
Haka nan kuma ana sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta ba wa kungiyar Taliban tabbaci na shiga cikin yaki da kungiyar IS.
Na biyu kuma watakila mafi mahimmancin yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabancin siyasar Kabul.
Da yammacin ranar Asabar, Ma’aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta ba da wata sanarwa tana cewa, wakilinta na zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake yin kutsawa cikin yankin yana neman tsallake fara wadannan shawarwari, wanda aka maimaita jinkirta yayin da bangarorin biyu ke takaddama kan shirin sakin fursunonin.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ke marawa baya ta bukaci gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunoni ‘yan Taliban 5,000 da kuma‘ yan Taliban din don ‘yantar da ma’aikatan gwamnati da na soja 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawa zai nuna alama kafin tattaunawa.
Har ya zuwa yanzu gwamnati na kin sakin fursunonin Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira manyan masu aikata laifi kuma ta yi tayin ba da wasu zabi na daban.
Kungiyar Taliban ta ki yarda.
