Babban bankin Burtaniya HSBC ya musanta "kafa tarko" ga Huawei na China a binciken Amurka - Labarin Kasuwanci na RT
Babban bankin HSBC mai hedikwata a Landan ya yi amfani da kafofin sada zumunta inda ya ce ba haka bane, kamar yadda kafofin yada labaran China suka ce, "kirkirar hujja" a kan Huawei, wanda ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudi na kamfanin a Canada.
A wani sakon da ba a samu yanzu ba a WeChat, mai ba da lamunin ya ce ayyukan da ta yi ba su haifar da binciken Amurka ba a kan babbar kamfanin da ke samar da kayayyakin sadarwar sadarwa a duniya ba, kamar yadda bincikar kamfanin Huawei kan zargin karya takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya wa Iran ya fara tun kafin bankin ya shiga cikin marigayi 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wata kiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba ta" tsara "Huawei ba," in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, yana mai kara da cewa ba zai taba gurbata wata hujja ba game da abokan huldarta.
"Dangane da bukatar US DOJ ta [Ma'aikatar Shari'ar Amurka] na neman bayanai, HSBC Group kawai ta gabatar da hakikanin abin da aka sa gaba.
HSBC ba ta "ƙirƙira" shaidu ko "ɓoye" gaskiyar ba. "
Hakanan a kan rt.com yunƙurin UK na hana Huawei daga hanyar sadarwa na 5G ya nuna Amurka ta nuna manufofin ƙetare na Burtaniya - George Galloway zuwa Boom Bust
An toshe sakon a dandamali tare da bayanin cewa "ya saba ka'idoji" kuma babu shi yanzu.
Wannan bayanin ya zo ne jim kadan bayan kafofin watsa labarai da yawa na kasar Sin, ciki har da jaridun da ke da nasaba da gwamnati, suka zargi HSBC da "hada baki" da Washington don shirya wa Huawei tarko.
Kamfanin ya kasance a tsakiyar cibiyar badakalar diflomasiyya fiye da shekara da rabi tun lokacin da aka kama Huawei CFO Meng Wanzhou a watan Disambar 2018 a Kanada bisa sammacin Amurka.
Meng na fuskantar tuhumar zamba kan zargin yin amfani da kamfanin harsashi don karya takunkumin da aka sanya wa Iran da kuma zargin yin karya ga bankuna game da alakar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran na Skycom.
A cikin sabon shaidar da Global Times ta ambata, HSBC tana sane da alaƙar kamfanin China da Skycom.
Bankin ya bayar da rahoton cewa ya zabi "hada baki" da gwamnatin Amurka don guje wa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya amince da shigar da kudaden haram da karya takunkumi, gami da takura wa Iran.
An umarce shi a lokacin da ya biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 a matsayin fansa kuma don hana kowane irin ɗabi'a mara kyau.
"Shaidun sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantakar amma da gangan ta sayar da bayanan sirrin abokan cinikinta ga bangaren Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka ta iya yin watsi da rashin da'a da bankin na Burtaniya ya yi ba tare da ladabtar da ita ba a karkashin Yarjejeniyar da Aka Kaddamar da Laifuka na 2012," in ji jaridar a cikin daya daga cikin labaran ta game da lamarin.
A cikin gargadin da ta rufe, jaridar da ke karkashin kulawar Beijing ta kara da cewa, mai bayar da bashin, idan har aka tabbatar da laifin wannan "hadin bakin," na iya fuskantar "azaba mai tsanani" a China, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwannin HSBC.
Ba wannan ba ne karon farko da shahararren bankin ya sha suka a makonnin da suka gabata.
A watan da ya gabata, HSBC ta kasance cikin ladabi saboda tallafawa sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa ta Hongkong, garin da kasuwancin ta ya fara kuma wanda ke dauke da fiye da rabin ribar sa.
Bankin ya fuskanci suka daga bangarorin biyu - daga Yammacin duniya, inda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira amincewa a matsayin "kamfani kowtow," da Gabas, in da rahotanni suka ce bangaren na China na cewa goyon bayan nasa "ya yi jinkiri."
'Yan kwana-kwana sun yi nasara a kan wutar Lassen County
