Bayan da aka shafe kwanaki hudu ana wuta, wutar ta laka ta kadada dubu 21, ta lalata gidaje bakwai sannan ta tura jami’an kashe gobara biyu zuwa asibiti.
A cikin dare, masu kashe gobara sun yi amfani da yanayi mai sauƙi don ginawa da ƙarfafa layukan sarrafawa.
Amma ana tsammanin iska mai sanyi da ƙarancin zafi zuwa Asabar.
