Gobarar ta lafa cikin dare yayin da masu aikin kashe gobara ke aiki don yin laushi da ƙarfafa layukan sarrafawa, a cewar Ma'aikatar Daji da Kare Gobara ta California.
Zuwa safiyar Asabar, ya kasance kashi 45% kuma an kone shi tsawon kwanaki shida.
A cikin zafin rana, tare da yanayin zafi sama da digiri 90 a yankin Susanville, facin da ke cin wuta yana cikin haɗarin yin sama.
Duk da yake ana ba wasu mazauna izinin komawa gidajensu, wasu yankuna a duka yankunan wuta suna ci gaba da kasancewa ƙarƙashin umarnin ƙaura.
An sallami 'yan kwana-kwana biyu da suka ji rauni a gobarar Zinariya daga asibiti.
