Zanga-zangar Seattle: Gobara da barkono suna fesawa kamar dubunnan Maris Suna Wuraren Gari
SEATTLE - Bayan makonni da aka kwashe ana gumurzu tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., Taron mutane kimanin 2,000 sun yi taro a Seattle ranar Asabar, suna tafe a kan tituna suna taho mu gama da ‘yan sanda.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti sakamakon rauni da ya samu a jikinsa, kuma an kama masu zanga-zangar 16 har zuwa yammacin ranar,' yan sanda sun ce.
Masu dauke da alamomi kamar su ''Jami'ai Su Koma Gida" da kururuwar ihun "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya," masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da za a tsare matattarar matasa nan gaba kuma suka kunna wuta a gine-ginen wurin.
Wasu sun farfasa tagogin wuraren kasuwancin da ke kusa.
‘Yan sanda sun yi fito na fito da jama’ar a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka baza gurneti da barkonon tsohuwa kafin su fara daukar mutane a tsare.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, daga Kirkland, Wash., Ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce yana da matukar damuwa a gare ta ganin irin wannan dabarun 'yan sanda.
"Wannan ba kasar da na yi hijira ba ne," in ji Madam Mukherjee, wacce ta zo daga Indiya sama da shekaru 30 da suka gabata.
"Yana ji kamar muna hanzarin zama jihar masu ra'ayin fascist da kuma jihar 'yan sanda."
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar an yi ta ne ga hukumomin yankin da kuma tura jami’an gwamnatin tarayya da suka yi wata zanga-zangar adawa da zanga-zangar da aka dade ana yi a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dabarun tilasta bin doka a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye da kuma abubuwan da mutane ke sarrafawa, na da hadari kuma bai dace ba.
