Bayan wasu harbe-harbe a can ya sa ‘yan sanda sun share yankin, zanga-zangar ta lafa.
Portland, a halin yanzu, na ci gaba da zanga-zangar, tare da wasu zanga-zanga mafi tsanani a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a cikin birnin.
Bayan Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Cikin Gida ta tura tawagogin dabaru zuwa cikin gari, inda aka fara jerin rikice-rikicen da ya haifar da jikkata masu zanga-zangar, binciken babban sufeto da kira daga shugabannin yankin ga wakilan tarayya tafi.
Jama'a masu zanga-zanga a wannan birni sun cika dubbai, kuma ana ci gaba da yin zanga-zangar a can.
