Majalisar Dattawa za ta kunshi mambobi 300, 100 daga cikinsu an zabi su ne ta hanyar jerin sunayen da aka rufe, 100 kuma ta hanyar tsarin mutum ne suka zaba, da kuma mambobi 100 da Shugaban Jamhuriyar ya nada
Wa'adin zama memba a majalisar dattijai zai kasance shekaru biyar, farawa daga ranar taronta na farko.
Za'a zabi sabon majalisar ne a cikin kwanaki sittin gabanin karshen wa'adinta.
Jami'an 'Yan sanda na gwada sabbin kayan aiki, masu saurin kisa yayin ci gaba da zanga-zangar
Yayinda ake ci gaba da artabu tsakanin jami’an tsaro da masu zanga-zanga a garin Portland da kewaye, ana ta cece-kuce game da yadda ‘yan sanda za su rage karfin yin kisa.
Wasu kamfanoni suna tashi don ba da sabbin kayan aikin zamani kamar ɗamarar hannu don 'yan sanda su yi amfani da su maimakon zaɓuka masu haɗari kamar fesa barkonon, harsasan roba da kuma gurneti mai walƙiya.
Kungiyar kare hakkin dan adam ta Amnesty International ta binciko bidiyo 500 daga zanga-zangar daga 26 Mayu zuwa 5 na Yuni kuma ta gano abubuwa 125 na zartar da karfi fiye da kima a jihohin 40 da Gundumar Columbia.
"Mun ga yadda aka yi amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye, barkonon tsohuwa, barkonon barkono, zagaye na milimita 40, asalima duk wani hadadden makamin da ba na kisa ba da ake amfani da shi ta hanyoyin da ba su dace ba," in ji mai binciken makamai na Amnesty International Brian Castner.
Duk da haka, wasu sun nace cewa samun zaɓuɓɓuka na da mahimmanci don guje wa buƙatar bindiga.
Corey Pegues, tsohon New ya ce "Duk wadannan na'urori ya kamata su kasance a hannun 'yan sanda don amfani da wasu karfi na karfi da bindiga ke amfani da shi saboda ita ce kadai sana'ar da Amurka ke ba' yan kasarta damar ba ka damar daukar ranka." Mataimakin Sifeto Yan Sandan York.
Daya daga cikin sabbin kayan aikin shine ake kira Bola Wrap, na’urar hannu wacce ke harba igiyar Kevlar mai kafa 8 wacce ke zagaye da wanda ake zargi.
Akwai Na'urori Masu Nisan Tafiya, wanda aka fi sani da suna canons, ana tura makamai masu ƙarfi waɗanda ke amfani da lasers don dumama fatar mutum, sabbin abubuwa da aka yi daga abubuwa kamar kumfa da alli, bama-bamai masu ɗoyi, kuma tabbas Taser.
Hannun jari na Axon, kamfanin da ke yin Taser, yayi sama da 18%, ya kai kowane lokacin da zanga-zangar ta rikide ta zama 'yan kwanaki bayan kisan da' yan sanda suka yi wa George Floyd.
Kasuwar makamai marasa saurin kisa ana harsashen zai kai dala biliyan 11.85 nan da shekarar 2023.
Dubi bidiyon don kallon sabbin kayan aikin zamani da 'yan sanda ke amfani da su don karfi da kisa, yadda ake tsara su, da abin da ke cikin hadari ga makomar' yan sanda da kuma al'ummomin da suke yi wa aiki.
Magajin garin Kansas City yana maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen warware kashe-kashe, amma ya damu da dalilan Trump
Magajin garin Kansas, Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi kan dalilan Shugaba Trump na tura wakilan tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen magance kashe-kashen da aka yi a garin na Midwest, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama kawai game da siyan damar sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon ganin [cewa] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci batun Black Lives Matter," Lucas, dan Democrat, ya ce a "Fox News Lahadi" na zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da bambancin launin fata da kuma zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Abin ba haka yake ba a Kansas City. Mun samu karin shekara-shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kansa shi ne share wasu kashe-kashen da ba a magance su ba."
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari muyi kokarin nuna wata alama da kuma niyya kan warware kashe-kashe ... Ina ganin idan kun saurari bayanan na baya-bayan nan ... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da wakilan tarayya a cikin wata iyaka."
Duk da yardar sa wakilan tarayya su yi aiki tare da jami'an tsaro na gari, Lucas ya ce kalaman Trump - musamman dangane da takaddama da ta dabaibaye dabarun da aka yi amfani da su a Portland, Ore., Daga wakilan tarayya - ya sa da yawa daga mazabarsa sun bayyana damuwarsu kasancewar wakilai a titunan birni.
"Abin da ba mu bukata shi ne karin mai a kan wutar daga wakilan tarayya don yin, ina tsammanin, batun siyasa ne mai kayatarwa," in ji shi.
Turi a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura wakilan gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance hauhawar yawan laifuka - lamarin da ke nuna fadada tsoma bakin fadar White House a cikin jami'an tsaro na cikin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin "doka da oda" shugaban kasa.
'' Hawan '' wakilai da aka sanar ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka wani bangare ne na shirin 'Legend Legend' - wanda aka sanya wa sunan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka harbe har lahira yayin da yake barci a wani gida a Kansas City a ƙarshen watan da ya gabata.
Duk da yake aika wakilan tarayya don taimakawa masu bin doka ba abu ne da ba a taba gani ba - Babban Lauya Bill Barr ya ba da sanarwar irin wannan kokarin a cikin watan Disamba ga garuruwa bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin wakilin da ake aikawa na tarayya, da wasu dabarunsu, sun tayar da damuwa tsakanin yan majalisar jiha da na kananan hukumomi.
Wasu ‘yan majalisa daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana game da gwamnatin Trump da ta tura wakilai zuwa garuruwansu, musamman biyo bayan rahotannin da ke cewa jami’an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san su ba sun tsare masu zanga-zangar a Portland kuma sun tafi da su a cikin motocin da ba su da tambari.
Portland ta sha fama da zanga-zangar kusan-kowace rana ta nuna adawa da zaluncin 'yan sanda da tsarin wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare a hannun' yan sanda na Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
Har ila yau, hukumomin yankin sun koka da cewa hawan da ake yi ya kara dagula lamura ne kawai, kuma masana harkokin shari’a masu aikata laifuka sun ce kokarin ya saba wa bayani saboda lokacin da ba a taba ganin irin sa ba a Amurka - tare da annoba, rashin aikin yi na tarihi da kuma yawan lissafi kan wariyar launin fata da kuma yadda mutane masu launi suke kula da 'yan sanda.
AP ta caccaki sakatariyar yada labarai ta Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany saboda "bayanin siyasa" - amma masu rahoto sun ci gaba da yin tambayoyin siyasa - RT USA News
Kamfanin dillacin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakatariyar yada labarai ta Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwar kafafen yada labarai ta hanyar sanya bayanan nata a siyasance maimakon na fadakarwa - da alama ta manta cewa ‘yan rahoto ne suka zabi tambayoyin.
Wani labarin a ranar Asabar da AP, kamfanin dillancin labarai mafi girma a Amurka, ya ce taron manema labarai na Fadar White House na iya zama "gurbatacciyar al'ada ce," kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "ingantacciyar hanyar talla ce ta shugaban kasa da ke fuskantar sake zaben, wurin da za a hare-hare kan kafofin yada labarai da kuma dandalin da ke da haske kan bayanai "game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
Waɗannan ra'ayoyin ba za a iya jayayya dasu ba, kamar yadda da wuya a bayyana wani sabon bayani a cikin taƙaitaccen bayanin.
Abin da AP ta kasa ambata shi ne cewa da wuya a nemi sabon bayani a zahiri.
Masu rahoto suna amfani da latsa Fadar White House don jan hankali zuwa ga kansu, fasalin fasaha wanda CNN's Jim Acosta ya tsara.
Sun wuce dangantakar abokantaka ta hanyar sadarwa tsakanin gwamnatoci, suna maimaita juna wajen yin tambayoyi wasu marasa amfani da nufin kawai su roki Shugaba Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna yiwa kansu labarai ne, kamar lokacin da wakilin CBS News Weijia Jiang ya amsa martani da "tambaya China" daga Trump ta hanyar yin wata magana mara ma'ana game da wariyar launin fata: "Yallabai, don me kuke faɗi haka a gare ni musamman? "
Wani bayani na 6 ga Yuli ya ba da babban misali na yankewa kan yadda bayanin ya daina zama tushen tushe mai ma'ana ga Amurkawa.
Trump ya wallafa a shafin sa na Twitter cewa safiyar ranar cewa an cutar da kimar talabijin na NASCAR saboda zargin karya na laifin nuna kiyayya ga direba Bubba Wallace da kuma hukuncin da ta yanke na hana nuna tutar kungiyar ta Confederate a yayin taronta.
A bayyane yake, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin mai rahoto bayan mai rahoto ya yi wa McEnany tambayoyin da aka tsara don tunzura ta ta ce Trump na goyon bayan tutar edeungiyar.
McEnany bai bayar da amsar da 'yan jarida ke so ba - cizon sautin da zai cutar da Trump - amma ta maimaita amsa da cewa shugaban ba ya daukar matsayi a kan tutar kungiyar' yan tawaye kuma dalilin da ya sa sakon shi ne cewa magoya bayan NASCAR sun kasance ba daidai ba bayyana a matsayin mai nuna wariyar launin fata.
AP din ta ce ta yi 'kara' lokacin da take bayani.
Labarin AP din ya bayyana a shafin Washington Post a farkon wannan watan daga wakilin ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shi ne shugaban kungiyar 'Yan Jarida ta Fadar White House.
Karl ya yi jayayya, "musun gaskiya da amfani da farfajiyar Fadar White House don dalilai na siyasa kawai keta hurumin amanar jama'a ne."
Duk da haka saurin saurin McEnany da salon fada sun sanya ta zama jarumar wasu magoya bayan Trump, tun lokacin da ta fara gabatar da jawabinta na farko a ranar 1 ga watan Mayu bayan ta karbi sakatariyar yada labarai a watan Afrilu.
'Yan jaridar ba su halarci taron ba sama da shekara guda kafin nadin nata.
Kamar sauran fannoni na rayuwar siyasa a Washington, dangantakar sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House da kafofin watsa labarai ya canza sosai a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canjin ya zo ne daga ɓangarorin biyu kuma ya gabaci zuwan McEnany.
Gasar da tsohuwar sakatariyar yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders ta yi daga mai barkwanci Michelle Wolf a Fadar White House Wakilan "abincin dare a watan Afrilu 2018 ya munana sosai har ma mai masaukin MSNBC Mika Brzezinski ya kira ta" abin takaici. "
Wakiliyar AP Fadar White House Jill Colvin ta gaishe da McEnany a jawabinta na farko ta hanyar tambaya, "Shin ba za ku yi alkawarin ba za ku taba yi mana karya ba daga wannan dandalin?"
Masanin harkokin siyasa na Fox News Brit Hume, gogaggen dan sama da shekaru 50 a aikin jarida wanda ya yi aikin 1989-1996 a matsayin babban wakilin ABC na fadar White House, ya ce 'yan jarida a yau suna nuna "halayyar fada" a cikin dakin tattaunawa saboda yadda suka raina Trump.
Saboda mayar da hankalinsu ga adawa da Trump ne, ya ce wannan makon a shirin Fox na Tucker Carlson na Daren yau, ‘yan jarida suna sakaci wajen tattara labaran siyasa.
"Wannan ba wasa ba ne kawai," in ji Hume game da maƙasudin maƙasudin matsafan.
"Ba wai kawai wani yunƙuri ne na kunyata wani jami'in gwamnati ba. An yi hakan ne don ciro bayanai."
An ga wasu barorin Safari da ke dauke da wukake, masu leken asiri da kuma jaridar CHAINSAW a matsayin 'yan iska da ke ba su makamai don lalata motocin'
Bayanai na farko a filin shakatawa na Knowsley safari, Merseyside, an daɗe da sanin su fadowa kan duk wanda ya tsaya a cikin shingen kuma ya cire gilashin gilashin gilashi ko madubi.
