Karuwar da aka samu a lokuta, yayi dai-dai da annashuwa game da ragowar jagororin kulle-kulle a yankunan da ba a kayyade kasar, ya sanya Indiya ta zama ta uku a jerin kasashen da abin ya fi shafa.
Amurka kawai (laka 41,78 lakh) da Brazil (23.94 lakh) sun fi rauni.
Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia ya nada sabon PM, domin kafa gwamnati cikin wata daya
An nada Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia Hichem Mechichi don kafa gwamnati mai zuwa, in ji ofishin shugaban kasar, a daidai lokacin da rikicin siyasa ke faruwa tsakanin manyan jam’iyyu a kasar ta Arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 46 ya gaji Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin Firayim Minista a farkon wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi ba ya daga cikin sunayen da jam’iyyun siyasa masu mulki suka gabatar wa Shugaba Kais Saied.
A wata sanarwa da ya biyo bayan sanarwar ta ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "yi aiki don kafa gwamnatin da za ta cimma burin dukkan 'yan Tunusiya"
An yaba wa Tunisia a matsayin labarin da ba a cika samun nasara ba game da canjin dimokiradiyya bayan boren kasashen Larabawa na yankin wanda ya haifar da juyin juya halin shekarar 2011.
Amma shugabanninta sun sha wahala don biyan bukatun mutanen Tunisia kuma tattalin arzikin da ya riga ya tabarbare ya sha fama da rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta kamu da fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Bayan kasancewarsa ministan cikin gida a cikin gwamnati mai barin gado, Mechichi ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga Shugaba Saied, yana kula da lamuran doka.
Ya taba zama shugaban ma’aikata a Ma’aikatar Sufuri sannan ya kuma yi aiki a Ma’aikatar Harkokin Jama’a.
Yanzu yana da wata guda don kafa gwamnati, wanda daga nan zai fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa da majalisar dokoki kuma zai bukaci cikakken rinjaye don yin nasara.
Idan ba haka ba, za a rusa majalisar sannan a sake gudanar da sabon zabe cikin watanni uku.
A zabukan karshe da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta hau kan karagar mulki amma ta kasa samun mafi yawa kuma daga karshe ta amince ta shiga cikin gwamnatin hadaka.
Murabus din Fakhfakh a ranar 15 ga watan Yulin, bayan kasa da watanni biyar kan karagar mulki, ya yi barazanar sake barkewar siyasa a cikin kasar yayin da take fama da matsalar tattalin arziki na annobar.
Murabus din ya zurfafa rikicin siyasa da Ennahdha kan zarge-zargen da ake yi wa Fakhfakh na rikice-rikicen sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaban mai barin gado da Ennahdha mai shekaru 47 ya tabarbare tun bayan zaben majalisar dokoki na Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a wannan ranar da jam'iyyar ta gabatar da bukatar rashin amincewa da shi.
Da farko Ennahdha ya zabi wani mai zaman kansa na Firayim Minista, amma ya kasa samun goyon bayan majalisar, lamarin da ya sa shugaban kasar ya nada tsohon Ministan Kudi Fakhfakh a mukamin.
Gabanin yiwuwar sake sabon zabe, daga karshe Ennahdha ya yarda ya shiga gwamnatin hadaka.
Mota ta wuce cikin jama'a, an harbi mai zanga-zanga a cikin Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Mota ta bi ta cikin jama'a kuma an harbe wani mai zanga-zanga a cikin garin Denver na kewayen Aurora yayin zanga-zangar adawa da rashin adalcin launin fata.
Ofishin ‘yan sanda na Aurora ya fada a shafin Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya ne a kan babbar hanyar ta 225 ranar Asabar lokacin da abin hawa ya wuce.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zangar ya harba makami, inda ya buge akalla mutum daya da aka kai shi asibiti cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Hukumomi sun ce an ja motar kuma suna ci gaba da bincike.
‘Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar sun kuma fasa tagogi a harabar kotun kuma an fara wuta a cikin wani ofishi.
An bayyana taron haramtacce kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zangar su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
Tashin hankali ya ta'azzara a zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da rashin adalcin launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don dakatar da zanga-zangar a Portland, Oregon.
‘Yan sanda sun ayyana tarzoma a Seattle ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da ta biyo bayan mutuwar 25 ga watan Mayu na George Floyd, wani bakar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani jami’in farar fata ya rike shi a kasa tare da gwiwa zuwa wuyansa, sun kuma nuna wasu batutuwa na tashin hankalin ‘yan sanda.
A cikin Colorado, masu zanga-zangar sun ja hankali game da mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka tsayar yayin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan mai kiran 911 ya ba shi rahoton cewa yana tuhuma.
'Yan sanda sun sanya shi a cikin wani yanki, kuma masu ba da agajin gaggawa sun ba da miligram 500 na ketamine, mai kwantar da hankali, don kwantar da hankalinsa.
Ya shiga cikin kamawar zuciya, daga baya aka ayyana shi kwakwalwa ya mutu kuma ya cire tallafin rai.
Canjin tafkin Tahoe ya zama gurɓatacce saboda canjin yanayi
Kudancin Lake Tahoe, California - Duk da cutar, ko da a ranar mako, mutane har yanzu suna cincirindon Paparoma a Tafkin Tahoe.
Wata yarinya mai suna Dakota ta ce "Ina son yin zango da tuka keke da zuwa iyo a Tekun."
Emerica Benitas ta ce "Wannan wani kyakkyawan abu ne da kowa ke son ziyarta."
Abin da ya sa har yanzu kasuwancin Matt Meunier ke ci gaba da ƙarfi, koda a cikin annoba.
Ya ce yana ganin "tsabtar tsabta. Tabkin Tahoe shi ne mafi tsafta, mafi ban mamaki tafki, a ganina, a cikin ƙasar."
Yanzu labari mara dadi: Tabkin Tahoe bashi da tsafta, ba mai haske bane, kamar yadda yake ada idan ya koma nan sama da shekaru ashirin da suka gabata.
Meunier ya ce "Abubuwan da muke lura da shi da yawa suna kan duwatsu,"
"Kuna samun irin wannan algae mai ban al'ajabi akan duwatsu."
Canjin yanayi, masana kimiyya sunyi imani, ya shafi zafin ruwan kuma don haka, tsabta.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 suna ziyartar tafkin duk shekara - tare da datti da suke barinwa.
Meunier ya ce tafiye-tafiyen nutsewa don tsaftace ƙasan tafkin da aka samo tsofaffin shara.
Meunier ya ce "Kuma idan na ce tsohon shara, ina nufin '60s, 70s,'
"Gwanon giya, gwangwani, gwangwanin cocin daga tsohuwar zamanin."
Masana kimiyya suna lura da bayyane tafkin Tahoe kowace shekara ta hanyar sauke farin diski, sa'annan su auna yadda zasu iya ganinta.
Farfesan UC Davis, Geoff Schladow, ya ce wannan '' muhimmiyar manuniya ce ta yadda tabkin yake da lafiya. ''
Lokacin da aka auna shi a bara, bayyananniyar tabkin yakai ƙafa 80.
Wannan yana nufin za ku iya ganin faifan 80 ƙafa ƙasa.
Amma, la'akari da wannan, kimanin shekaru 20 da suka gabata, bayyananniyar tabki yakai ƙafa 100.
Wannan shine yanayin da masana kimiyya ke ƙoƙarin juyawa.
Amma suna fada ne da tasirin canjin yanayi, ci gaba a kusa da tabkin da wani abu da aka kara wa tabkin a shekarun 1960: Wani karamin tsire-tsire masu banƙyama da aka kawo don ciyar da kifin.
Bai yi aiki ba.
"Da zarar shrimp ta shigo, ba zato ba tsammani babu masu tsabtace yanayi a cikin tafkin," in ji Schladow.
Irin wannan kalubalen na fuskantar tabkuna da jikkunan ruwa a duniya.
"Darasin da ke nan shi ne, idan ba za ku iya yi a Tahoe ba, to mene ne fata ga dukkan koguna da wuraren hawan kawara, magudanan ruwa da tafkuna a kewayen ƙasar waɗanda ba za su taɓa samun digiri iri ɗaya ba, irin matakin albarkatu? " Schladow ya ce.
Meunier ya ce yana da "fata" saboda "idan akwai rufin azurfa na annobarmu, ina tsammanin hakan ya nuna cewa dabi'a za ta dawo ta warkar da kanta idan har kawai mun sauƙaƙe wannan matsin lamba, na ɗan adam, kashe shi kuma muka bari hakan ta faru. Akwai hujjoji a wurin yanzu. "
Ma'aurata MACED a wurin shakatawar kare na California saboda rashin sanya maskin fuska yayin cin abincin rana (BIDIYO) - Labarin RT USA
Akwai abun rufe fuska sannan kuma akwai cika kan hari.
Wasu ma'aurata 'yan Kalifoniya da ke cin abincin rana tare da kuruciyarsu a wurin shakatawa na kare sun sami na biyun, lokacin da wata mace mai haushi ta watsa musu barkono saboda kin rufe fuska ... yayin cin abinci.
Ash O'Brien da mijinta Jarett Kelley sun ce suna kama cizon da za su ci a gidan shakatawar Dusty Rhodes da ke San Diego a ranar Alhamis, tare da jaririnsu dan wata uku.
Ma'auratan sun rufe masks don su ci abinci, lokacin da "tsohuwa tsohuwa" ta zo, tana kiran su "wawaye" don ba su yin kwalliya, duk da cewa "ba za ku iya sanya abin rufe fuska ba ku ci a lokaci guda."
O'Brien ta ce wa matar ta bar wurin shakatawar kuma ta daina muzguna mata, a lokacin ne matar ta saki gwangwanin mac a ma'auratan.
Hotunan bidiyo da wani mai kallo ya dauka ya fara ne da Kelley yana kokawa da maganin feshin daga mace, da kuma samun maganin mata a fuska don matsalolinsa.
Ana iya jin O'Brien tana kuka a bango yayin da maharin ke tafiya da karnenta.
O'Brien ta raba bidiyon a Facebook kuma ta gaya wa ABC 10 cewa tana son ganin matar "ta tafi gidan yari."
Abun rufe fuska dole ne a duk faɗin jihar Kalifoniya, koda da iska mai iska.
Ana iya cire waɗannan masks kawai a wasu zaɓaɓɓun lokuta, gami da lokacin ci ko sha.
Koyaya, babu inda ke cikin jagororin coronavirus na jihar da yake cewa masu tsayayyar na iya amfani da muggan makamai marasa ƙarfi don aiwatar da wannan manufar.
Ko da a wannan zamanin da ake ciki na "rufa-rufa," wannan har yanzu laifi ne da ke dauke da hukuncin tarar dala 1,000 ko kuma zuwa shekara uku a kurkukun jihar.
Scotland-England Union Chain Bridge tana da shekaru 200
Wata gada da ta hada Scotland da Ingila ta cika shekaru 200 kafin a gyara fan miliyan 10.
Gadar Union Chain ta ratsa Kogin Tweed daga Fishwick a cikin Yankin Scottish zuwa Horncliffe a Northumberland.
Lokacin da aka buɗe shi a 1820, ita ce gada mafi tsayi da aka dakatar da baƙin ƙarfe a duniya tare da tsawon 449ft (137m).
Hakanan ita ce gada ta farko ta ababen hawa irinta a cikin Burtaniya.
Jami'in sojan ruwa na kasar Ingila Capt Samuel Brown ne ya tsara gadar.
Ya mallaki kamfani kuma ya samar da sarƙoƙin ƙarfe bayan asarar jiragen ruwa na Royal Naval waɗanda suka yanke daga igiyoyi ya shafa shi.
Abokai na Union Chain Bridge da kuma ofungiyar Injiniyan Civilasa (Ice) Scotland suna ta yin bikin shekara biyu da hayewa.
Robert Hunter, na kungiyar abokai, ya ce: "Wannan hakika daya daga cikin gadoji mafi tarihi a duniya kuma wani bangare ne na kere kere.
“Mun shirya wasu bukukuwa da dama don murnar wannan ranar, amma abin takaici dole ne a daga su.
"Duk da haka, gaskiyar cewa aiki zai fara kan gyaran £ 10m shine mafi kyaun ranar haihuwar da zai yiwu kuma zai tabbatar da tsararraki masu zuwa za su iya jin daɗin gadar a duk ƙawarta."
Daraktar Iceland Hannah Smith ta bayyana gadar a matsayin wani yanki da "ba a kula da shi" wani bangare na kayayyakin aikin injiniya na Scotland.
Ta ce: "Mun san sanannen duniya ne kuma yana da ban sha'awa cewa nan ba da jimawa ba za a fara aikin gyara shi."
Barkewar cutar Salmonella tana cutar da mutane 212 a cikin jihohi 23
25 ga Yuli (UPI) - Cibiyoyin Kula da Rigakafin Cututtuka na binciken barkewar cutar salmonella wacce ta yi wa mutane 212 rashin lafiya a cikin jihohi 23 na kasar.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar a ranar Juma'a CDC ta ruwaito cewa mutane 87 sun kamu da rashin lafiya tun bayan sabuntawar da ta yi kan bullar cutar a ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane sun fara nuna alamun alamun da ke da nasaba da kwayar cutar salmonella, wacce za ta iya daukar makonni biyu zuwa hudu kafin bayyanar alamun, tsakanin 19 ga Yuni da 11 ga Yuli.
An kwantar da mutane talatin da daya a asibiti tun lokacin da cutar ta fara, amma ba a samu asarar rai ba.
A cewar CDC, ba a gano wani takamaiman tushe don cutar salmonella ba.
Ba ta ba da wata sanarwa ba game da cin ko cinye wasu abinci, ko masu sayar da kayayyaki waɗanda za su iya siyar da gurɓatattun kayayyaki.
Oregon ya sami mafi yawan lokuta na salmonella, tare da cututtuka 51, tare da Utah yana biye da baya tare da rahoton rahoton 40.
Salmonella cuta ce ta kwayar cuta, cututtukan abinci da ke haifar da cututtuka miliyan 1.35, kwantar da asibiti 26,500, da kuma mutuwar 420 kowace shekara, a cewar CDC.
Mafi yawan alamun cututtukan salmonella sune gudawa, zazzabi, da ciwon ciki, wanda zai iya farawa tsakanin awanni shida da kwanaki shida bayan fallasa.
Rashin lafiyar galibi yana ɗaukar kwanaki huɗu zuwa bakwai, kuma yawancin mutane suna warkewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu lokuta suna buƙatar asibiti.
United, Chelsea cikin CL; Bournemouth, Watford daga EPL
